Gtkmathview Qt Port

mml-view-qt in the qwidget based viewer. Currently only one-time rendering supported.

Compile && Install

install default opentype math font XITS MATH
https://github.com/khaledhosny/xits-math

install autoconf, automake, gcc, qt5, libxml2, etc.

run autoconf
$ ./autogen.sh

configure with qt
./configure --enable-gtk=no --enable-qt=yes

compile and install
make -j4 && sudo make install

Usage

mml-view-qt path/to/mathml/xml

